Subprog AS_MEDORG(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(46228,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_MEDORG(zc) From W1HRMAT10
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_MEDORG(zc) From W1HRMAT10
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_MEDORG(zc) From W1HRMAT10
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_MEDORG(zc) From W1HRMAT10
